ğŸ”‘ KEY DECISIONS
â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€

When to use Pickle?
  âœ“ Python-only projects
  âœ“ Performance critical
  âœ“ Complex Python objects
  âœ— Untrusted data sources
  âœ— Cross-language communication

When to use JSON?
  âœ“ Web APIs and REST
  âœ“ Untrusted data (safe)
  âœ“ Cross-language
  âœ“ Human-readable
  âœ— Complex Python objects
  âœ— Datetime/custom types

When to use YAML?
  âœ“ Configuration files
  âœ“ Human readability
  âœ“ Comments support
  âœ— Performance-critical
  âœ— Large data sets

